description: Defines the MaintenanceEvent class used for tracking vehicle maintenance events within a fleet management app. Includes properties, constructors, serialization, and copy methods.

classes.name: MaintenanceEvent
classes.description: Model class representing a maintenance event related to a vehicle, with properties like id, vehicleId, type, status, dates, description, cost, notes, and colorCode.

methods.name: MaintenanceEvent.fromMap
methods.description: Factory constructor that creates a MaintenanceEvent instance from a map, typically sourced from a database.

methods.name: MaintenanceEvent.toMap
methods.description: Converts a MaintenanceEvent instance into a map for storage or serialization.

methods.name: MaintenanceEvent.copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of this MaintenanceEvent with optional updated fields.
